org.matsim.core.router.util

Class PreProcessLandmarks

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.core.router.util.PreProcessDijkstra
      • org.matsim.core.router.util.PreProcessEuclidean
        • org.matsim.core.router.util.PreProcessLandmarks

  • public class PreProcessLandmarks
extends PreProcessEuclidean
    Pre-processes a given network, gathering information which can be used by AStarLandmarks when computing least-cost paths between a start and an end node. Specifically, designates some nodes in the network that act as landmarks and computes the last-cost-path from and to each node in the network to each of the landmarks.
    Author:
    lnicolas
